Case Based, Theory

Explanation: 
- Case Based: The paper presents a PAC analysis of a case-based reasoning algorithm called V S-CBR. It discusses how the algorithm collects cases and adjusts a weighted similarity measure. 
- Theory: The paper applies the PAC learning framework to analyze the hypothesis spaces of the learner on different target concepts and explores the constituent parts of the instance-based learner. It also discusses the overall behavior of the algorithm in relation to its constituent parts.
